<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Text</title>
    <style>
        div {
            width: 800px;
            height: 300px;
            border: 2px solid black;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 22px;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: 2px;/*harfler arası bosluk*/
            word-spacing: 3px;/*kelimeler arası bosluk*/
            line-height: 200%;
        }
        h2{
            text-transform: capitalize;/*ilk harfler büyük*/
            text-transform: uppercase;/*büyük harf*/
        }
        span{
            font-style: italic;
            color: blue;
            font-weight: bold ;
        }
        a{
            color: darksalmon;
            text-decoration: none;

        }
        a:hover{
            color: blue;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div>
        <h2>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur.</h2>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor <span> <a id href="http://www.google.com" target="_blank"> sit amet </a></span> consectetur adipisicing elit. Maiores delectus itaque inventore. A earum numquam
            mollitia et! Quia vero atque unde, at in natus, sequi molestias nesciunt nobis odio nostrum?</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>